OL,3,CSouthampton man jailed for rape and
OL,4,Csexual assault
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for the rape of
OL,7,Fa woman at a house in Southampton
OL,8,Fearlier this year.
OL,10,F26 year old Thomas Antony Drew, from
OL,11,FGolden Grove, was sentenced to three
OL,12,Fyears and four months in prison.
OL,14,FDrew is subject to a Sexual Harm
OL,15,FPrevention Order with strict
OL,16,Fconditions for seven years, and will
OL,17,Fhave a restraining order, meaning he
OL,18,Fwill not be able to make contact with
OL,19,Fthe victim for 15 years.
