OL,6,FThe woman involved, who is in her 30s,
OL,7,Freported to police that in the early
OL,8,Fhours of 27 February she was with Drew
OL,9,Fat a house in Southampton when he
OL,10,Fforced himself upon her and raped her.
OL,12,FAt a Southampton Crown Court hearing
OL,13,Fin July, he pleaded guilty to one
OL,14,Fcount of rape and one count of sexual
OL,15,Fassault by penetration.
