OL,6,FIn a statement read to the court, the
OL,7,Fvictim said that Drew had abused her
OL,8,Ftrust in the most devastating way
OL,9,Fimaginable, and that what happened to
OL,10,Fher had impacted both her mental and
OL,11,Fphysical health.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,14,FDetective Constable Georgina Harris
OL,15,Ffrom Hampshire Police, who led the
OL,16,Finvestigation, said: "Drew's actions
OL,17,Fhave understandably had a significant
OL,18,Fand traumatic effect on the woman he
OL,19,Fraped and assaulted.
