OL,6,F"While I know that no court outcome
OL,7,Fcan change what she has had to endure,
OL,8,FI do sincerely hope that Drew's
OL,9,Fimprisonment goes some way in helping
OL,10,Fher closure and recovery.
OL,12,F"I would like to add that I am
OL,13,Fincredibly grateful to the victim for
OL,14,Freporting what happened to her so
OL,15,Fswiftly, which meant we were able to
OL,16,Farrest Drew quickly and bring him
OL,17,Fbefore the courts to face the
OL,18,Fconsequences of his crimes. Without
OL,19,Fher courage we would not have secured
OL,20,Fthis outcome.
