OL,6,F"We take every report of rape and
OL,7,Fsexual assault made to us extremely
OL,8,Fseriously. We will investigate each
OL,9,Fone, no matter what the circumstances,
OL,10,Fand have specially trained teams to
OL,11,Finvestigate and provide support to
OL,12,Fvictims.
OL,14,F"We urge anyone who feels they have
OL,15,Fbeen a victim of rape, other sexual
OL,16,Foffences and domestic abuse to please
OL,17,Freport it to us or to a support
OL,18,Fservice. You will be listened to and
OL,19,Fyou will be supported."
